-----------------------------
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-----------------------------

mailq.php process the MTA queue to store messages in database and to see the in MailWatch GUI.

Put the mailq.php file in /usr/local/bin

Edit CRONTAB:

# crontab -e

# Run mailq.php each minute
0-59 * * * * 	/usr/local/bin/mailq.php

Note: mailq.php re-creates all entries on each run, so for busy sites you will probably want to change this to run every 5 minutes or greater.
